{"tid":119072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卑鄙！韋特文借隊友過橋呃對手","createTime":"2017-02-13T13:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T07:52:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83bebc6d5aa0ef93fbd5dfd40f9feac6bfbe6888","tid":119072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=decef58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周日荷甲出現欠缺體育精神一幕，阿積士後衛祖爾韋特文竟借隊友受傷倒地過橋，令敵將轉移視線，好讓自己可以繼續引球出擊。<br />\n<br />\n既然有公平競技獎，國際足協現可考慮增設不君子行為獎，得主一定是這位祖爾韋特文（Joel Veltman）。這位阿積士的副隊長，在周日荷甲對鹿特丹斯巴達的比賽，「出蠱惑」欺騙對手，且利用人家的同情心達致目的，行為十分可恥。<br />\n<br />\n當時，他正在邊線控著皮球，身前有一名敵衛看管他，而離他附近不遠，一名隊友在之前的碰撞後倒地不起，狀甚痛苦。韋特文此時示意對手，指有人受傷應暫停比賽，但竟趁對方稍有鬆懈，回頭望這位受傷球員時，突然加速在邊線快放，然後落底線傳中，幸上天有眼，這次攻勢最終未有造成入球。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到阿積士當時已領先2:0，不是落後一方，祖爾韋特文的行為更令人感到厭惡，未知荷蘭足總會否就此秋後算帳，判罰這位欠缺道德的球員。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1v9D7hpiDSQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1v9D7hpiDSQ&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e88022a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1v9D7hpiDSQ</a>"},{"pid":"5e1ffe572f2a8fe8dbb42ca6b098ca74cd7fde3a","tid":119072,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"倫敦賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdf3a024178d9897ec6d077ea142b786fb8078e","tid":119072,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"你話佢係香港人我都信"},{"pid":"1d2184519bb70ca5dda97809ec7e54878e72fe02","tid":119072,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"呢 d 真係斷腳收山最好"},{"pid":"1257c9ac7292a6905fb0675f559f32f9817187d8","tid":119072,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"2:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150df2a85034eca3f40a1112b053f76949ad0b04","tid":119072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3103ac2245913647c44c03b04ccb57dda76de40f","tid":119072,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"同奇狗有得揮"},{"pid":"0af67e5a97802d8d601801ac60cb75881d29db4c","tid":119072,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0135e7e46e2a7ec63f7793ee52d0d1bca6e98c18","tid":119072,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}